2.11	Aristomenis_Tsirbas	Aristomenis Tsirbas	Aristomenis Tsirbas (born 1967, Montreal, Canada) is a film director, producer, writer, animator and visual effects animator. He is well known for directing the award winning short films The Freak and Terra which was adapted into the 2007 feature film of the same name produced by MeniThings Productions and Snoot Entertainment.	
